Making Piña Coladas with Halfday Tropical Tea, Pineapple @‌fruitriot & Organic Coconut @‌malkorganics might’ve just changed our lives…

Here’s how we did it:
🍍 Fill a blender with Halfday Tropical Tea, ice, @‌malkorganics Organic Coconut milk, Pineapple @‌fruitriot, and lime juice
🍍 Blend and pour into a scooped-out whole pineapple
🍍 Top with an optional rum floater
🍍 Garnish with pineapple leaves and an umbrella straw
